# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok peoplesoft announced plans monday to buy jd edwards in a #.# billion dollar stock deal to create the world 's second-largest provider of enterprise applications software .
# ::alignments
(a / announce-01
      :ARG0 (c / company
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Peoplesoft"))
      :ARG1 (p / plan-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (b / buy-01
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 (c2 / company
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Jd"
                              :op2 "Edwards"))
                  :ARG4 (d / deal-01
                        :ARG0 c
                        :ARG2 (c3 / create-01
                              :ARG0 c
                              :ARG1 (c4 / company
                                    :ARG0-of (p2 / provide-01
                                          :ARG1 (s / software
                                                :mod (a2 / application
                                                      :mod (e / enterprise))))
                                    :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                                          :ARG2 (l / large)
                                          :ARG3 (m / most
                                                :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                                                      :value 2))
                                          :ARG5 (w / world)))
                              :mod (s2 / stock))
                        :ARG3 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                              :quant 1000000000
                              :unit (d2 / dollar))))
            :time (d3 / date-entity
                  :weekday (m3 / monday))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok c.j. niusulu was granted a delay to the remaining time on his work-release sentence , the result of an altercation a few years ago in barstow , enabling him to participate in ucla 's first workout wednesday .
# ::alignments
(g / grant-01
      :ARG1 (d / delay-01
            :ARG1 (t / time
                  :ARG1-of (r / remain-01)
                  :duration-of (s / sentence-01
                        :ARG1 (p / person
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "C."
                                    :op2 "J."
                                    :op3 "Niusulu"))
                        :ARG2 (r2 / release-01
                              :ARG1 p
                              :ARG2 (w / work-01))))
            :ARG2 p
            :ARG1-of (r3 / result-01
                  :ARG2 (f / fight-01
                        :time (b / before
                              :op1 (n2 / now)
                              :quant (f2 / few
                                    :op1 (t2 / temporal-quantity
                                          :quant 1
                                          :unit (y / year)))
                              :location (b2 / barstow))
                        :ARG0-of (e / enable-01
                              :ARG1 (p2 / participate-01
                                    :ARG0 p
                                    :ARG1 (w2 / workout-01
                                          :ARG0 (p3 / person
                                                :name (n3 / name
                                                      :op1 "Ucla"))
                                          :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                                                :value 1)
                                          :time (w3 / wednesday)))))))
      :ARG2 p)

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok three people , including two children , were reportedly stabbed and killed on friday when a man went on a killing rampage in a nursery in a northern belgian town , flemish broadcaster vrt reported .
# ::alignments
(r / report-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "vrt")
            :ARG0-of (b / broadcast-01)
            :mod (f / flemish))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (s / stab-01
                  :ARG1 (p2 / person
                        :quant 3
                        :ARG2-of (ii / include-91
                              :ARG1 (c / child
                                    :quant 2))))
            :op2 (k / kill-01
                  :ARG1 p2)
            :ARG1-of r)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f2 / friday))
      :time (g / go-on-15
            :ARG0 (m / man)
            :ARG1 (r2 / rampage-01
                  :ARG0 m
                  :ARG1 k))
      :location (n2 / nursery
            :location (t / town
                  :location (n3 / north
                        :part-of (c2 / country
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Belgium"))))))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok wall street shares drifted lower tuesday after fresh data showed american consumer confidence fell unexpectedly in september .
# ::alignments
(d / drift-01
      :ARG1 (s / share
            :mod (m / market-sector
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Wall"
                        :op2 "Street")))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday))
      :time (a / after
            :op1 (s2 / show-01
                  :ARG0 (d3 / data
                        :ARG1-of (f / fresh-04))
                  :ARG1 (f2 / fall-01
                        :ARG1 (c / confidence
                              :poss (p / person
                                    :ARG0-of (c2 / consume-01)
                                    :mod (c3 / country
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "America"))))
                        :ARG1-of (e / expect-01
                              :polarity -)
                        :time (d4 / date-entity
                              :month 9))))
      :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
            :ARG2 (l / low-04
                  :ARG1 d)
            :ARG3 (m2 / more)))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :op1 "China"))

            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (t / trouble-01
                  :ARG0 (p / politics)
                  :time (g / game
                        :mod (c2 / continent
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Asia"))))
            :condition (w2 / withdraw-01
                  :polarity -
                  :ARG1 (ii / invite-01
                        :ARG1 (p2 / person
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Lee"
                                    :op2 "Teng-hui")
                              :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG1 (c3 / country
                                          :name (n4 / name
                                                :op1 "Taiwan"))
                                    :ARG2 (p3 / president)))
                        :ARG2 g)))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t2 / thursday)))

# ::id 5 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

      :ARG0 (c / chain
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Carrefour")
            :ARG0-of (d / distribute-01
                  :ARG1 (r / rench)))
      :ARG1 (a / amount-01
            :ARG1 (t / turnover
                  :ARG1-of (c2 / consolidate-01)
                  :poss c
                  :ARG2-of (ii / include-01
                        :ARG1 (t2 / tax)))
            :ARG2 (m / monetary-quantity
                  :quant 1000000000
                  :unit (f / franc))
            :time (y / year
                  :mod (l / last))
            :ARG1-of (u / up-02
                  :ARG3 (p / percentage-entity
                        :value "1/3")
                  :ARG4 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                        :quant 1000000000
                        :unit (d2 / dollar)))
            :source (l2 / level
                  :ARG1-of (r2 / release-01)))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (m3 / monday)))

# ::alignments

      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "rene"
                  :op2 "Lavrov")
            :ARG0-of (s2 / support-01
                  :ARG0-of (m / make-02
                        :ARG1 (f / favor-01
                              :ARG0 (m2 / mass
                                    :mod (p2 / poor))
                              :ARG1 p
                              :ARG2 (b / become-01
                                    :ARG1 p
                                    :ARG2 (p3 / president
                                          :ARG2-of (h / have-org-role-91
                                                :ARG0 p
                                                :ARG1 (s3 / state
                                                      :name (n2 / name
                                                            :op1 "Hiti"))
                                                :mod (n3 / next)))))))
            :ARG1-of s2)
      :ARG2 (o / out-06
            :ARG1 p
            :ARG2 (s4 / silence
                  :ARG1-of (b2 / begin-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :time (a / after
                              :op1 (e / elect-01
                                    :time (w / week
                                          :mod (l / last))))))
            :purpose (c / charge-06
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG2 (s5 / stain-01
                        :ARG0 (a2 / and
                              :op1 (d / defraud-01
                                    :mod (m3 / massive))
                              :op2 (e2 / err-01
                                    :ARG1-of (g / gross-06)))
                        :ARG1 (p4 / process-02))
                  :time (d2 / date-entity
                        :weekday (t / tuesday)))))

      :ARG0 (b / bureau
            :topic (s / statistics)
            :mod (n / nation)
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Portuguese")))

            :ARG1 (d2 / deficit
                  :mod (t / trade-01
                        :ARG0 c
                        :ARG2 (o / organization
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "European"
                                    :op2 "Union")
                              :mod (e / euro
                                    :polarity -))))
            :ARG2 (p / percentage-entity)))

                  :mod (s2 / space)
                  :poss (c3 / country
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "France"))
                  :location (p / province
                        :name (n5 / name
                              :op1 "Guiana")
                        :part-of (c4 / continent
                              :name (n6 / name
                                    :op1 "Europe"))))
            :ord (o2 / ordinal-entity
                  :value 1)
            :ARG1-of (s3 / schedule-01
                  :ARG3 (e / end-01
                        :ARG1 (t / thing
                              :name (n7 / name
                                    :op1 "####")))
                  :time (ii / initial))
            :time (n8 / now)
            :time (q / quarter
                  :ord o2
                  :value 4))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t2 / tuesday)))

# ::id 1801 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the us economy grew at an annual #.# percent in the second quarter , the commerce department reported friday in a final estimate .
# ::alignments
(r / report-01
      :ARG0 (g / government-organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Commerce"
                  :op2 "Department"))
      :ARG1 (g2 / grow-01
            :ARG1 (e / economy
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name n
                        :op1 "US")))
      :ARG2 (r2 / rate-entity-91
            :ARG1 (p / percentage-entity
                  :value 1)
            :ARG2 (t / temporal-quantity
                  :quant 1
                  :unit (y / year)))
      :time (q / quarter
            :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                  :value 2))
      :location (e2 / estimate-01
            :mod (f / final))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f2 / friday)))

# ::id 1802 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok foreign minister manouchehr mottaki renewed on saturday iran 's readiness for negotiations over its nuclear proposals but made no direct response to calls from the major powers for urgent talks .
# ::alignments
(r / renew-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Manouchehr"
                  :op2 "Mottaki")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG2 (m / minister
                        :topic (f / foreign))))
      :ARG1 (r2 / ready-02
            :ARG1 (c / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Iran"))
            :ARG2 (n3 / negotiate-01
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG2 (t / thing
                        :ARG1-of (p2 / propose-01
                              :ARG0 c)
                        :mod (n4 / nucleus))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s / saturday))
      :concession-of (r3 / respond-01
            :polarity -
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (c2 / call-03
                  :ARG0 (p3 / power
                        :ARG1-of (m2 / major-02))
                  :ARG1 (t2 / talk-01
                        :mod (u / urgent))
                  :ARG2 c)
            :ARG1-of (d2 / direct-02)))

# ::id 1803 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (t / tour-01
                  :ARG1 (w / wall
                        :mod (g / great)
                        :location (a / area
                              :mod (c / city
                                    :name (n / name
                                          :op1 "Beijing"))))))
      :ARG1 (f2 / fine-01
            :ARG1 (u / up-to
                  :op1 u
                  :op1 (a2 / and
                        :op1 (m / monetary-quantity
                              :quant 1000000
                              :unit (y / yuan))
                        :op2 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                              :quant 10000000000
                              :unit (y2 / yuan))
                        :op3 (m3 / monetary-quantity
                              :ARG1-of (w2 / worth-01
                                    :ARG2 (d / dollar))))))
      :condition (c2 / climb-01
            :ARG0 p
            :location (p2 / part
                  :ARG1-of (a3 / authorize-01
                        :polarity -)
                  :part-of (s / site
                        :mod (h / heritage
                              :mod (w3 / world))))))

            :weekday (t / tuesday)))

                  :ARG0-of (l2 / legislate-01)
                  :mod (e / ethnic-group
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Nepali"))
                  :ARG1-of (a / arrest-01
                        :ARG2 (c2 / charge-05
                              :ARG1 p
                              :ARG2 (m / murder-01
                                    :ARG0 p
                                    :ARG1 (b / businessman)))))
            :ARG1 (ii / innocent-01
                  :ARG1 p))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s / sunday)))
